	* src/spi_stm32.c (cyg_spi_cortexm_stm32_init): mark as
	prioritized constructor and rename.

	* cdl/spi_stm32.cdl: stop building spi_stm32_init.cxx

	* src/spi_stm32_init.cxx: removed, no longer needed.

